PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports' political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Lise McNally asks
OL,8,Fwhether the government's plans will
OL,9,Fmake the grade.
OL,11,FSeveral parents in the North West say
OL,12,Fthey are concerned about the new
OL,13,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,14,Fdisabilities (SEND) reforms.
OL,26,@oD@Prt
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FGovernment estimates suggest that
OL,7,Fapproximately one in eight children
OL,8,Fwith special educational needs and
OL,9,Fdisabilities (SEND) who currently
OL,10,Freceive the highest level of support
OL,11,Fwill move to new plans between 2030
OL,12,Fand 2035.
OL,14,FThese estimates are included in a
OL,15,Fseries of reforms designed to make
OL,16,FEngland's SEND system more inclusive,
OL,17,Frepresenting a move away from the
OL,18,Fcurrent trend of increasing placements
OL,19,Fin costly specialist schools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FKimberly Hind's five-year-old son
OL,7,FHarvey recently started attending a
OL,8,Fspecialist school after losing much of
OL,9,Fhis eyesight and hearing.
OL,11,FThe mother, from Clitheroe, says there
OL,12,Fare many issues with current SEND
OL,13,Fprovisions, but reducing the reliance
OL,14,Fon specialist schools is not the
OL,15,Fanswer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FShe said: "He had zero confidence
OL,7,Fthroughout mainstream (school), he
OL,8,Fstopped eating, he stopped sleeping,
OL,9,Fhe would self-destruct... And we
OL,10,Factually had to get a specialist to
OL,11,Fhelp us to go out of the front door
OL,12,Fbecause he was so afraid of the world
OL,13,Faround him.
OL,15,F"Now, I mean, we've seen ourselves
OL,16,Fthis morning, he ran out of the door
OL,17,Ffor school, his speech has come on.
OL,26,@oD@WpmoD@^pn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,F"He's a different child. And I know
OL,7,Fyou can only take my word for that,
OL,8,Fbut many families are experiencing not
OL,9,Feven getting these provisions at all.
OL,10,FAnd it's heartbreaking, it's
OL,11,Fheartbreaking."
OL,13,FIn England, if they need more support
OL,14,Fthan is typically provided in
OL,15,Fmainstream schools, their parent or
OL,16,Fcarer can apply for an education,
OL,17,Fhealth and care plan (EHCP), which
OL,18,Fsets out the extra support they are
OL,19,Fentitled to.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FHarvey, who is in year one, does have
OL,7,FEHCP, but his mother fears the new
OL,8,Fproposals will have an impact on his
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FChildren who are currently in year
OL,12,Fthree or above will keep their EHCP
OL,13,Funtil at least age 16.
OL,15,FThose in year two or below will be
OL,16,Freassessed when they move to secondary
OL,17,Fschool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FKimberley said, "We live that struggle
OL,7,Fand if any of that was to be taken
OL,8,Faway from us or stripped back or...
OL,9,FHarvey doesn't cope well with any
OL,10,Fchange..
OL,12,F"I fear we will be back to square one."
OL,14,FNaomi Sykes, a neurodivergent single
OL,15,Fparent to eight-year-old Harry, is
OL,16,Fdeeply concerned about the direction
OL,17,Fof special educational needs and
OL,18,Fdisabilities (SEND) provision under
OL,19,Fthe government's proposed reforms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FHarry is autistic and has ADHD, and
OL,7,Fdespite being "extremely bright", he
OL,8,Fstruggles with "very profound and
OL,9,Fcomplex needs in terms of his social,
OL,10,Femotional and mental health."
OL,12,FNaomi stresses that "there should be
OL,13,Fno ceiling to what he should be able
OL,14,Fto achieve," but insists that
OL,15,Feducation must be "incredibly
OL,16,Fnurturing and respectful of his need
OL,17,Ffor autonomy."
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@POUrD@]O]tD@UOUvD@LO]wD@SOUyD@
OL,26,ANO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FNaomi said, "Me and many families and
OL,7,Fprofessionals are greatly concerned...
OL,8,Fit could quite easily see all sectors
OL,9,Fof education moving backwards rather
OL,10,Fthan forwards."
OL,12,FShe describes the exhausting fight for
OL,13,Fsuitable support, stating, "I feel
OL,14,Flike I have to bend over backwards and
OL,15,Fgo way beyond what is within my means
OL,16,Fto be able to compromise for what
OL,17,FHarry actually needs... when it should
OL,18,Fjust be a right for every child to be
OL,19,Fable to thrive."
OL,21,FWhy are SEND reforms needed?
OL,26,@nD@MOUrD@OO]uD@\OU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,7,Fthe current system "does not work" for
OL,8,Fchildren and parents, with Education
OL,9,FSecretary Ms Phillipson saying too
OL,10,Fmany parents are having to "fight" for
OL,11,Fthe right support for their child.
OL,13,FSpending on support for children with
OL,14,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,15,Fdisabilities (SEND) has ballooned in
OL,16,Frecent years amid rising demand,
OL,17,Fleading to spiralling costs for
OL,18,Fcouncils and large deficits.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@bO]rD@\OUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FParents in the North West say more
OL,7,Fparents are having to stop work to
OL,8,Ftend to their childrens with little
OL,9,Fsupport provided in their plans.
OL,11,FThey say more specialist training is
OL,12,Frequired for mainstream facilities to
OL,13,Fbe able to provide adequate education,
OL,14,Fhealth and care needs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FThe government wants to have a more
OL,7,Finclusive system, with the reforms
OL,8,Fpledging to provide "inclusive
OL,9,Fmainstream alongside high-quality
OL,10,Fspecialist provision" through schools
OL,11,Fwhich are "equipped and funded to
OL,12,Fsupport children with Send to achieve
OL,13,Fand thrive in inclusive mainstream
OL,14,Fsettings, working together with high-
OL,15,Fquality specialist provision".
OL,17,FSo what are the proposed reforms?
OL,26,@pD@UOUrD@UO]sD@KOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fpromised education, health and care
OL,8,Fplans (EHCPs), a legal document
OL,9,Fsetting out the support children with
OL,10,FSEND are entitled to, will stay "for
OL,11,Fchildren with the most complex needs
OL,12,Fwill stay".
OL,14,FMainstream schools will receive direct
OL,15,Ffunding to support SEND children as
OL,16,Fpart of a #4 billion package, to make
OL,17,Fthe system more inclusive, including
OL,18,Finvestment in training for adaptive
OL,19,Fteaching styles.
OL,26,@rD@aOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FSome #1.6 billion over three years
OL,7,Fwill be provided to early years,
OL,8,Fschools, and colleges through an
OL,9,F"inclusive mainstream fund".
OL,11,FWhile another #1.8 billion over the
OL,12,Fsame period will go towards creating
OL,13,Fan "experts at hand" service, made up
OL,14,Fof specialists such as SEND teachers
OL,15,Fand speech and language therapists in
OL,16,Fevery area.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@[O]uD@DOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,FThe White Paper sets out to change the
OL,7,Fcurrent legal rights of children with
OL,8,Fless severe needs and instead
OL,9,Festablish a new tiered structure for
OL,10,Fsupporting SEND children, based on the
OL,11,Flevel of their need.
OL,13,FThe proportion of children with SEND
OL,14,Fon the current highest level of school
OL,15,Fsupport is projected to start falling
OL,16,Feach year from the end of the decade.
OL,18,FMaking a speech at a school in the
OL,19,FEast Midlands, Phillipson said,
OL,20,F"Forget the misinformation you might
OL,21,Fhave heard.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771949050
OL,3,CParents with special needs children
OL,4,C'concerned' by SEND reforms
OL,6,F"EHCPs for children with the most
OL,7,Fcomplex needs will stay, guided by
OL,8,Fnationally defined and evidence-based
OL,9,Fspecialist provision packages."
OL,11,FIn summary;
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/16
